This is a small but useful module for Kohana 3.

Some basic documentation here: http://wiki.github.com/glydetech/ko3.xhtml/
Forum Post here: http://forum.kohanaphp.com/comments.php?DiscussionID=4701

Version 0.1 (2010-01-25)
 - Basic operation
 - Xhtml singleton class
 - Head singleton class
 - Abstract Controller_Xhtml extending Controller_Template
 - Mapping controller $template to body
 
 Version 0.2 (2010-01-28)
 - Adjusted defaults handling, now global configs are overwritten by controller properties
 - Added an ajax property to the controller
 - Added check for template property to before()

Version 0.3 (2010-02-01)
 - Recoded to use extended views instead of extended template controller
 
Version 0.4 (2010-02-07)
 - Recoded to use main Xhtml and Head classes instead of extended views
 - Wrapped all inline scripts with CDATA
 - Adjust tags without content to use appropriate closing syntax based on content type
 - Added the file parameter to the Xhtml class to auto-load into the body tag
 - Adjusted to use only lang or xml:lang in html tag based on content type
 - Detected the accept headers for content type determination

Version 0.5.1 (2010-02-28)
 - Added defaults array to Head instance
 - Added chainable functions
 - Added merged and cached scripts and styles
 - Added controller for serving caches
 - Added tidy